This package vendors the LIBSVM C++ implementation from e1071 1.7-17
for the scop CIBERSORT C++ backend. Symbols are prefixed with
`cibersort_` to avoid conflicts with e1071 when both packages are loaded.

e1071 DESCRIPTION credits:

  Chih-Chung Chang [ctb, cph] (libsvm C++-code)
  Chih-Chen Lin [ctb, cph] (libsvm C++-code)

e1071 is distributed under GPL-2 | GPL-3. scop is distributed under
GPL (>= 3), so this vendored source is redistributed under GPL-3 terms
within scop.
